@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
title Governance action, end to end

|Proposer|
start
:author one of the seven action types;
:attach an anchor (metadata URL + hash)
and a refundable deposit (govActionDeposit);
:submit as an on-chain transaction;

|Voting bodies|
:action goes Live for govActionLifetime
(6 epochs on mainnet);
fork
  :DReps vote Yes / No / Abstain;
fork again
  :CC votes (constitutionality);
fork again
  :SPOs vote (their action types);
end fork

|Ledger|
if (thresholds met for this type?) then (yes)
  :Ratified at the epoch boundary;
  :Enacted at the next boundary
(change takes effect);
else (no)
  :Expired;
endif
:deposit returned to the
proposer's reward account;
stop
@enduml
